
---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | DreamMeaningGuide" description="DreamMeaningGuide.site is a calm, trusted resource for exploring the deeper meaning behind your dreams.">
  <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; color: #e8e0ff; font-family: Inter, sans-serif;">
    <h1 style="font-family: Cinzel, serif; font-size: 2.6rem; color: #d8c8ff; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">About</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      DreamMeaningGuide.site is a calm, trusted resource for exploring the deeper meaning behind your dreams.
      Our mission is simple: to help you understand the symbols, emotions, and patterns that appear in your
      inner world with clarity, insight, and a sense of wonder.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      We believe dreams are more than random images. They are messages, metaphors, and reflections of your inner life.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      DreamMeaningGuide is part of <strong style="color: #c4b5fd;">The Meaning Atlas</strong>, a growing network of sites dedicated
      to helping people explore symbols, signs, and spiritual meaning across many traditions.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      Whether you're curious about a recurring dream, a powerful symbol, or a strange moment that stayed with
      you — we're here to help you interpret it.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>


